gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 117, Magic 99
gameRecap.excerpt: Milwaukee defeats Orlando, 117-99. For Milwaukee, Bobby Portis led the way with 30 points, nine rebounds, and a career-high five steals while aided by Damian Lillard (29 points, six rebounds, nine assists) in the victory. Cole Anthony finished with 23 points, four rebounds, and four assists with Paolo Banchero adding 20 points, six rebounds, and six assists for Orlando in the losing effort. Milwaukee improves to 49-31, while Orlando moves to 46-34 in the loss.
